This paper discusses multilingual topic models and their evaluation, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of metrics and adaptation models, which are related to information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (LG, AI, DL).
